Borders Wins Bankruptcy Court Approval for Revised Executive Bonus Plan

-- B y   T i f f a n y   K a r y
-- 
2011-04-22T20:35:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-22/borders-wins-bankruptcy-court-approval-for-revised-executive-bonus-plan.html
Borders Group Inc. won approval for
an amended executive bonus plan, as the bankrupt bookstore chain
also withdrew its request to assume some employment agreements,
according to court papers filed today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
